{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a4471940df","title":"和续范亭的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b5150bdc74","index":0,"year":1944,"month":4,"day":30,"articleId":"a4471940df"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"09ee9b8e78","type":"paragraph","text":"和续范亭的谈话”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"a4471940df"},{"id":"621c3f14fb","type":"paragraph","text":"1944年4月30日）韩信在登坛拜将以前，还在汉中当过“粮食部长”。朱总司令自述他初做军官就充当司务长，旧日司务长正是管连队生活，并负训练与作战的责任。现在我们的大将们都研究粮食问题，全体指战员都亲自动手，建立各单位的大小家务。各部首长、干部不但都能管理军队生活，而且都能直接参加生产，这是全世界军队没有的奇迹，同时也是中国军队的大改革，这对革命是一件很大的事。[1]这是毛泽东关于粮会对战争的重要性和续范事谈话的一部分。续范","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"a4471940df"}],"page":{"id":"676c1ea7f7","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"a4471940df","start":441,"end":441}}}},"__N_SSG":true}